{"tid":2102373,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"法德提歐盟反制港區國安法建議 但不制裁中國","createTime":"2020-07-10T11:58:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-11T12:25:24.000Z","uid":53003,"like":2,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"84b7f9afdc3157ee28507eb74e89bd84999c367c","tid":2102373,"uid":53003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T11:58:50.000Z","msg":"香港中通社7月10日電 題：法德提歐盟反制港區國安法建議 學者指為壓力下表態<br />\n<br />\n  香港中通社記者 張婕舒<br />\n<br />\n  針對《港區國安法》，美國主導的五眼聯盟國家接連出台反制措施，而此前被指態度保守的歐盟也有跟進跡象。據《金融時報》10日引述歐盟外交消息報道，法國和德國已提出首項歐盟反制措施建議。歐洲問題研究學者認為，歐盟是迫於內外壓力而作出表態，與美國藉機打壓中國有很大區別。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.hkcna.hk/content/2020/0710/837569.shtml\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkcna.hk%2Fcontent%2F2020%2F0710%2F837569.shtml&d=Wd2ZpPw6abVmqVF%2BhWwumhSC%2F35X4DTIU%2BW3we%2FDSDs%3D&h=a79f35c8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.hkcna.hk/content/2020/0710/837569.shtml</a>"},{"pid":"edf0a9d305cfea79618cdf9295174fc167a3f9c6","tid":2102373,"uid":6030,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T12:00:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Tafg9PS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTafg9PS.png&h=467cad69&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e597921238d962b195196ffb0722a26c3459163b","tid":2102373,"uid":26389,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T12:25:24.000Z","msg":"中國人買得最多法國名牌 老佛爺排滿曬大陸游客 法國點會制裁中國"}]}